OL,3,CFar-right groups are unchristian, says
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury has
OL,7,Flabelled the far-right "unchristian"
OL,8,Fand condemned the use of Christian
OL,9,Fimagery in the riots as "an offence to
OL,10,Four faith".
OL,12,FJustin Welby made the remarks
OL,13,Fcondemning the violent unrest, which
OL,14,Fhe described as "racist", "anti-
OL,15,FMuslim, anti-refugee", in an article
OL,16,Ffor the Guardian newspaper.
