OL,3,CFar-right groups are unchristian, says
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FThe country's most senior Christian
OL,7,Fleader weighed in following a week of
OL,8,Fdisorder that began after a mass
OL,9,Fstabbing of children at a Taylor Swift-
OL,10,Fthemed dance class in Southport in
OL,11,FJuly.
OL,13,FRioters attacked police, mosques,
OL,14,Fshops, and a hotel housing asylum
OL,15,Fseekers after incorrect rumours that
OL,16,Fthe suspect in the stabbings was an
OL,17,Fasylum seeker who arrived in the UK on
OL,18,Fa small boat were spread via social
OL,19,Fmedia, appearing to fuel the unrest.
