OL,3,CFar-right groups are unchristian, says
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FPolice had arrested 779 people in
OL,7,Fconnection with the rioting, the
OL,8,FNational Police Chiefs' Council said
OL,9,Fon Saturday.
OL,11,FThe archbishop's article centred on
OL,12,Fimploring Christians to distance
OL,13,Fthemselves from the far-right,
OL,14,Fwriting: "Let me say clearly now to
OL,15,FChristians that they should not be
OL,16,Fassociated with any far-right group `
OL,17,Fbecause those groups are unchristian."
