OL,3,CFar-right groups are unchristian, says
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FHe added that Christian iconography
OL,7,Fhad been "exploited" by the far-right
OL,8,Fand served as "an offence to our
OL,9,Ffaith".
OL,11,FSpeaking directly to Muslims and other
OL,12,Ffaiths, Mr Welby said: "We denounce
OL,13,Fpeople misusing such imagery as
OL,14,Ffundamentally antichristian."
OL,16,FMr Welby said the riots were
OL,17,F"detonated by lies and fuelled by
OL,18,Fdeliberate misinformation, spread
OL,19,Fquickly online by bad actors with
OL,20,Fmalignant motivations."
