OL,3,CFar-right groups are unchristian, says
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FHe went on: "The lies and
OL,7,Fmisinformation flourished in fertile
OL,8,Fground cultivated by years of rhetoric
OL,9,Ffrom some of our press and
OL,10,Fpoliticians, arriving at a point where
OL,11,Fsome felt emboldened to try to set
OL,12,Ffire to a hotel housing asylum seekers
OL,13,Fand target mosques."
OL,15,FThe archbishop also rejected the
OL,16,Fdescription of the riots as "protests"
OL,17,Fand said they were "criminal" and
OL,18,F"must be controlled".
