OL,3,CFar-right groups are unchristian, says
OL,4,CArchbishop of Canterbury
OL,6,FHe also praised efforts by the public
OL,7,Faimed at healing tensions, including
OL,8,Fan imam in Liverpool who offered food
OL,9,Fto a small group of protesters at a
OL,10,Fmosque and bricklayers in Southport
OL,11,Fwho helped to rebuild a mosque that
OL,12,Fhad been vandalised.
OL,14,F"We must develop and cherish these
OL,15,Fexamples of civic virtue that have
OL,16,Fbeen counter-messages to those of the
OL,17,Fmob," he said.
OL,19,FIt is not the first public statement
OL,20,Fthe archbishop has made on the recent
OL,21,Fdisorder.
